  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813;font-size:13px\">This is an optional class feature. Consult with your DM before adding this to your character.</em></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#191813\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><em>Replaces the Divine Strike or Potent Spellcasting feature</em></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#191813\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><em>When you reach 8th level, you are blessed with divine might in battle. When a creature takes damage from one of your cantrips or weapon attacks, you can also deal 1d8 radiant damage to that creature. Once you deal this damage, you can't use this feature again until the start of your next turn.</em></span></span></p>",
